        </div>
    </div>


    <br><br><br><br><br>

</div> <!-- /container full -->

<div class="container">

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="panel panel-default">

                <div class="panel-heading"><h3>{% trans %}about jolineck{% endtrans %}</h3></div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>
                        {% trans %}I was lost and afraid every time I had to play a rich chord like CMaj6(9|#11) or D7(#9|13).
                        All that stuff exceeded me!
                        How can I do?
                        I have only 4 fingers to play with on the neck (sometimes five with my thumb).
                        How to make sound all these fancy alterations?{% endtrans %}
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <a>{% trans %}read more ...{% endtrans %}</a>
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="panel panel-default">

                <div class="panel-heading"><h3>{% trans %}want to help{% endtrans %}</h3></div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>
                        {% trans %}You like this project. You can help us. We want to translate these webpages in most languages{% endtrans %}
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        {% trans %}You can also make a gift with paypal or bitcoins{% endtrans %}
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <a>{% trans %}read more ...{% endtrans %}</a>
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="panel panel-default">

                <div class="panel-heading"><h3>{% trans %}realbooks{% endtrans %}</h3></div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>
                        {% trans %}More than 2500 tune from 10 realbook completed{% endtrans %}
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <a>{% trans %}read more ...{% endtrans %}</a>
                    </p>
                </div>

